  ('medical-tech-moex-11289', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關癌症轉移之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["上皮癌（carcinoma），例如肺癌、乳癌，常轉移至局部淋巴結", "惡性肉瘤（sarcoma）之轉移僅靠血行轉移（hematogenous metastasis），不會有淋巴轉移現象", "上皮癌（carcinoma）若要具有轉移能力，其癌細胞常須先破壞基底膜（basement membrane）", "腦部多形神經膠母細胞瘤（glioblastoma multiforme），也有可能轉移至顱外其他器官"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cefd7cab5120", "answer_pdf_sha1": "330d47a38b87", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 52, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
