  ('medical-tech-moex-11292', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '移植器官對抗宿主疾病（graft-versus-host disease）最主要是由移植器官中的何種細胞所引起？', '["B 淋巴細胞", "T 淋巴細胞", "自然殺手細胞（natural killer cell）", "巨噬細胞（macrophage）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cefd7cab5120", "answer_pdf_sha1": "330d47a38b87", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 55, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11293', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '器官移植時經由直接路徑（direct pathway）機制所引起的細胞免疫急性排斥（cell-mediated acute rejection），主要是因為器官接受者之T淋巴細胞對移植器官中的何種細胞產生反應所致？', '["樹枝狀細胞（dendritic cells）", "T淋巴細胞（T lymphocyte）", "B淋巴細胞（B lymphocyte）", "實質細胞（parenchymal cell），例如肝臟之肝細胞"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cefd7cab5120", "answer_pdf_sha1": "330d47a38b87", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 56, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11294', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者是多囊性卵巢（polycystic ovaries）組織學或生化學上的特徵？', '["常出現單側卵巢腫大，至正常大小的兩倍以上", "血液中經常會出現高濃度的濾泡刺激激素（follicle-stimulating hormone, FSH）", "卵巢會出現許多大大小小的黃體囊腫（luteal cysts）", "血液中經常會出現高濃度的雄性激素（androgen）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cefd7cab5120", "answer_pdf_sha1": "330d47a38b87", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 57, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
