  ('medical-tech-moex-11296', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為婦女最常見的良性子宮腫瘤？', '["子宮平滑肌瘤（leiomyoma）", "子宮內膜息肉（endometrial polyp）", "子宮腺肌症（adenomyosis）", "子宮內膜間質結節（endometrial stromal nodule）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cefd7cab5120", "answer_pdf_sha1": "330d47a38b87", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 59, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
